公務員咁樣對市民會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n90年代之前啲公務員個個都係咁架啦<br />\n打後九鐵已經改革咗好多啦，個個講到臨合併仲係90年代咁款<br />\n九鐵啲職員起碼友善過依家啲閪面廢鐵職員</blockquote><br />\n改革成功就唔會兵變啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上係田北辰改革失敗加速兩鐵合併</blockquote><br />\n成唔成功睇你點睇，但九鐵後期的確係透明咗，最出名咪8分鐘通報機制<br />\n但一樣可以係田北辰自己太過急進而搞到所謂失敗<br />\n而且九鐵比依家既廢鐵更願意同大眾溝通，例如以前九鐵間唔中都搞下車廠開放日<br />\n依家廢鐵根本係唔憂做心態，仲駛乜同你地打好關係者</blockquote><br />\n九鐵仲有經常搞茶聚收集乘客意見 雖然唔知係咪真係有人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但起碼佢份月刊真係會講番有咁嘅嘢反應點樣同下一轉幾時同邊個站再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4879e4f0ad6cd3f645ea68b7e38179ad0e40d1b","tid":487310,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西鐵以前比人話係大白象<br />\n<br />\n過多十，今日比人叫大白象既野又會點</blockquote><br />\n西鐵都係延長左去尖沙咀先多咗人搭<br />\n以前南昌嗰個時候根本少人到痴線"},{"pid":"a568b3b81d099fa5e78eaead81cb04bcaea907ce","tid":487310,"uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqZEbjwqHexo&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI62xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d57c9169\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo</a><a href=\"https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqZEbjwqHexo&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI62xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d57c9169\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo</a><br />\n17:13 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果依家公務員咁樣對市民會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n90年代之前啲公務員個個都係咁架啦<br />\n打後九鐵已經改革咗好多啦，個個講到臨合併仲係90年代咁款<br />\n九鐵啲職員起碼友善過依家啲閪面廢鐵職員</blockquote><br />\n改革成功就唔會兵變啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上係田北辰改革失敗加速兩鐵合併</blockquote><br />\n成唔成功睇你點睇，但九鐵後期的確係透明咗，最出名咪8分鐘通報機制<br />\n但一樣可以係田北辰自己太過急進而搞到所謂失敗<br />\n而且九鐵比依家既廢鐵更願意同大眾溝通，例如以前九鐵間唔中都搞下車廠開放日<br />\n依家廢鐵根本係唔憂做心態，仲駛乜同你地打好關係者</blockquote><br />\n九鐵仲有經常搞茶聚收集乘客意見 雖然唔知係咪真係有人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但起碼佢份月刊真係會講番有咁嘅嘢反應點樣同下一轉幾時同邊個站再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果次西鐵火燭<br />\n之後即刻搞免費搭車<br />\n而且下個月月票減價<br />\n九鐵都仲識得補鑊<br />\n相反而家一句唔好意思算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f93268d63885894015a9d5990998797f2060df2","tid":487310,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n記得好多年前鏗鏘集有集講九鐵服務問題<br />\n節目訪問一個女乘客，佢覺得售票處某服務員態度有問題，打算投訴佢，於是問佢叫咩名<br />\n個職員咁答佢：「我做咩要話我個名你知啫，而家又唔係同你對親家」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqZEbjwqHexo&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI62xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d57c9169\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo</a><a href=\"https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqZEbjwqHexo&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI62xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d57c9169\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qZEbjwqHexo</a><br />\n17:13 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果依家公務員咁樣對市民會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n90年代之前啲公務員個個都係咁架啦<br />\n打後九鐵已經改革咗好多啦，個個講到臨合併仲係90年代咁款<br />\n九鐵啲職員起碼友善過依家啲閪面廢鐵職員</blockquote><br />\n改革成功就唔會兵變啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上係田北辰改革失敗加速兩鐵合併</blockquote><br />\n成唔成功睇你點睇，但九鐵後期的確係透明咗，最出名咪8分鐘通報機制<br />\n但一樣可以係田北辰自己太過急進而搞到所謂失敗<br />\n而且九鐵比依家既廢鐵更願意同大眾溝通，例如以前九鐵間唔中都搞下車廠開放日<br />\n依家廢鐵根本係唔憂做心態，仲駛乜同你地打好關係者</blockquote><br />\n九鐵仲有經常搞茶聚收集乘客意見 雖然唔知係咪真係有人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但起碼佢份月刊真係會講番有咁嘅嘢反應點樣同下一轉幾時同邊個站再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港鐵車廂意見區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50ea1c8367a2139942dc4a8afaecc32e17822ee","tid":487310,"uid":51720,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當年地鐵又真係管理得好過kcr好多</blockquote><br />\n個陣東鐵列車車底有裂紋要用人手駕駛<br />\n西鐵又火燭又成日壞<br />\n嚇死唔少人</blockquote><br />\n講到而家好好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 西鐵係少左壞<br />\n但而家到觀塘線成日壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前九鐵有8分鐘通報機制，人地主動報告你咪覺得成日壞囉<br />\n地鐵就鍾意收埋遲一遲先報<br />\n結果合併後就風水輪流轉，地鐵成日壞仲要收收埋埋唔公佈</blockquote><br />\n打壓及監控「非我族類」鐵路愛好者（原本就係未來鐵路公司員工潛在人物）；<br />\n無任何措施，讓乘客對鐵路認識，有「公開知」的權利（只能光顧鐵路學院）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c9fa601cc0924bfac02f0263fba4dfa1c9c3dd","tid":487310,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"我只係記得<br />\n鐘<br />\n欣<br />\n銅<br />\n路<br />\n西<br />\n呢個廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係移花接木十年喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9d237b1f33d57d799b4e4a94d3fb2cce45e806","tid":487310,"uid":78091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"Kcrc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e095b2ac3b495cb26710b04f818a17c4ba88653","tid":487310,"uid":5996,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十年都未慣叫港鐵</blockquote><br />\n根本就唔應該叫港鐵<br />\n火車同地鐵係交通工具<br />\n公司改左名都唔會改埋個交通工具既本質<br />\n你會唔會話九巴/ 城巴而唔係搭巴士"}]}